533
00:27:33.116 --> 00:27:35.277
It'll be fun.

534
00:27:35.351 --> 00:27:37.080
However, the next time you consider...

535
00:27:37.153 --> 00:27:41.920
attending a hearing over which I preside...don't!

536
00:27:45.428 --> 00:27:47.089
Committee is called to order.

537
00:27:47.163 --> 00:27:48.425
OK.

538
00:27:48.498 --> 00:27:50.591
Welcome to the special meeting of the Committee...

539
00:27:50.667 --> 00:27:53.431
