552
00:28:31.174 --> 00:28:32.698
in order to reunite Bruiser with his mother...

553
00:28:32.776 --> 00:28:34.403
in order to have them at my wedding...

554
00:28:34.477 --> 00:28:35.637
in which I was going to wear...

555
00:28:35.712 --> 00:28:38.306
the most perfect wedding shoes ever...

556
00:28:38.381 --> 00:28:40.849
right inside that box.

557
00:28:40.917 --> 00:28:44.944
They never covered this in the handbook.

558
00:28:49.959 --> 00:28:53.224
They're something, all right.

559
00:28:55.031 --> 00:28:56.362
You think?

560
00:28:57.600 --> 00:28:59.227
Oh, I'm sorry.

561
00:29:02.438 --> 00:29:04.736
Elle Woods, legislative aide...

562
00:29:04.808 --> 00:29:07.333
to Congresswoman Rudd, Massachusetts.

563
00:29:07.410 --> 00:29:10.402
Sid Post. Doorman.

564
00:29:10.480 --> 00:29:13.381
That door.

565
00:29:13.449 --> 00:29:16.577
