570
00:29:28.765 --> 00:29:33.225
with the Committee of En and Ron or whatever.

571
00:29:33.303 --> 00:29:35.362
Bye, Sid.

572
00:29:35.438 --> 00:29:39.067
-Comm. -What'd you say?

573
00:29:39.142 --> 00:29:42.908
