00:35:21.350 --> 00:35:22.783
Time to get serious.

681
00:35:22.852 --> 00:35:25.480
Subject--Congresswoman Libby Hauser.

682
00:35:25.555 --> 00:35:26.954
Came of age in Post-War boom...

683
00:35:27.023 --> 00:35:30.424
typified by 1951 Charles Jourdan stiletto heel.

684
00:35:30.493 --> 00:35:33.223
Moving up to the Texan's head, which is red...

685
00:35:33.296 --> 00:35:36.129
suspect chemical assistance. Must pursue.

686
00:35:36.199 --> 00:35:37.757
Hit me, Post.

687
00:35:37.833 --> 00:35:40.393
118 salons within a 10-mile radius...

688
00:35:40.469 --> 00:35:42.630
broken down by color expertise...

689
00:35:42.705 --> 00:35:48.075
and philosophical approach to hair maintenance and style.

690
00:35:48.144 --> 00:35:51.113
I didn't know you could have a philosophy of hair.

691
00:35:51.180 --> 00:35:52.477
Oh, yeah.

692
00:35:52.548 --> 00:35:54.846
Maybe that's where I went wrong.

693
00:35:56.419 --> 00:35:57.613
Go for Woods.

694
00:35:57.687 --> 00:35:59.450
It's just as you suspected.

695
00:35:59.522 --> 00:36:01.649
She's at a moderate conservative salon...

696
00:36:01.724 --> 00:36:04.158
founded on the principles of Vidal.

697
00:36:04.227 --> 00:36:07.219
In fact, it was one of our case studies...

698
00:36:07.296 --> 00:36:09.457
Iast year at Hair University.

699
00:36:09.532 --> 00:36:11.762
That was right before they flunked me.

700
00:36:11.834 --> 00:36:14.132
Paulette, they weren't ready for your vision.

701
00:36:14.203 --> 00:36:16.831
I know you'll make your mark hair-wise.

702
00:36:18.007 --> 00:36:19.474
Sorry.

703
00:36:19.542 --> 00:36:21.908
-You got a pen? -Yes.

704
00:36:21.978 --> 00:36:24.173
It's at Constitution and 12th.

705
00:36:24.247 --> 00:36:26.807
The Salon Bontempo.

706
00:36:30.186 --> 00:36:32.347
Don't you just love a salon day?

707
00:36:35.258 --> 00:36:38.819
Yes, so peaceful and quiet.

708
00:36:38.894 --> 00:36:41.192
Makes it so much easier to talk that way.

709
00:36:41.264 --> 00:36:42.822
They have rules about that here.

710
00:36:42.898 --> 00:36:45.526
I know. That's why I called to make sure...

711
00:36:45.601 --> 00:36:47.466
they used PETA-approved hair care products.

712
00:36:47.536 --> 00:36:49.697
When you think about what they do to those animals--

713
00:36:49.772 --> 00:36:51.831
Which is why I don't think about it.

714
00:36:51.907 --> 00:36:53.534
Does the trick.

715
00:36:57.480 --> 00:36:58.845
Excellent bobby pin handling.

716
00:36:58.914 --> 00:37:01.906
Thank you, Frederic. Looks great.

717
00:37:04.353 --> 00:37:06.150
Isn't it so comforting to see...

718
00:37:06.222 --> 00:37:08.213
they use eco-friendly foil technology here?

719
00:37:08.291 --> 00:37:10.885
Every planet needs a friend, that's what I always say.

720
00:37:10.960 --> 00:37:13.793
If I wanted to talk about the emotional life of a rock...

721
00:37:13.863 --> 00:37:16.696
you'd know it by now.

722
00:37:16.766 --> 00:37:19.200
Until this day, I'd held the highest opinion...

723
00:37:19.268 --> 00:37:21.964
of redheads as a fellow hair minority group.

724
00:37:22.038 --> 00:37:24.199
I heard quite enough of your politics...

725
00:37:24.273 --> 00:37:26.400
at the committee meeting, thank you very much.

726
00:37:43.926 --> 00:37:47.384
When was the last time you wore the yellow tea rose?

727
00:37:54.870 --> 00:37:57.134
I'm sorry? What did you just--

728
00:37:57.206 --> 00:37:59.640
When was the last time you wore your yellow tea rose?

729
00:37:59.709 --> 00:38:01.939
On the night of my initiation.

730
00:38:02.011 --> 00:38:04.206
Wasn't the passing of the secret scented eternal flame...

731
00:38:04.280 --> 00:38:06.874
of the goddess Delta Nu not the most moving experience?

732
00:38:06.949 --> 00:38:08.974
Especially the part where we sipped...

733
00:38:09.051 --> 00:38:11.713
from the secret pink chalice of sisterhood!

734
00:38:11.787 --> 00:38:13.516
Yes!

735
00:38:17.893 --> 00:38:20.054
Delta who?

736
00:38:20.129 --> 00:38:22.290
Delta Nu!

737
00:38:22.365 --> 00:38:25.596
Delta-Delta boo-gah-loo

738
00:38:25.668 --> 00:38:28.296
Nu Nu Delta

739
00:38:28.371 --> 00:38:29.702
Theta, Beta

740
00:38:29.772 --> 00:38:31.171
Lambda, Mu

741
00:38:31.240 --> 00:38:34.835
Ooh-aah, Delta Nu!

742
00:38:36.379 --> 00:38:39.542
Libby Hauser, Texas. Planning a wedding?

743
00:38:39.615 --> 00:38:42.516
That "l do" updo looks like heaven on you.

744
00:38:42.585 --> 00:38:43.745
Thank you.

745
00:38:43.819 --> 00:38:46.344
Who is he? Zeta Lambda Nu, I hope.

746
00:38:46.422 --> 00:38:48.515
Actually, I'm marrying outside the Greek system...

747
00:38:48.591 --> 00:38:50.320
but he's totally letter-worthy.

748
00:38:50.393 --> 00:38:54.830
But how is D.C. Elle-worthy?

749
00:38:54.897 --> 00:38:57.422
I'm here to speak for those who can't speak for themselves.

750
00:38:57.500 --> 00:38:59.468
How interesting.

751
00:38:59.535 --> 00:39:01.833
It's more than interesting. It's practical.

752
00:39:01.904 --> 00:39:04.270
Strictly a numbers game as far as you're concerned.

753
00:39:04.340 --> 00:39:09.937
125,468--Number of people in your district with dog licenses.

754
00:39:10.012 --> 00:39:13.948
12,762--The number of unemployed scientists...

755
00:39:14.016 --> 00:39:16.951
with the skills to develop alternatives to animal testing.

756
00:39:17.019 --> 00:39:21.683
And finally, 6285--the lD number of my dog's captive mother.

757
00:39:21.757 --> 00:39:24.885
I'm not sure I followed all that...

758
00:39:24.960 --> 00:39:26.450
but you got my attention.

759
00:39:26.529 --> 00:39:28.121
If there's one thing I know how to do...

760
00:39:28.197 --> 00:39:30.290
it's rinse and repeat. Shall we?

761
00:39:32.268 --> 00:39:33.428
Excuse me, do you happen to have a--

762
00:39:33.502 --> 00:39:35.493
-Get lost! -Excuse me, sir!

763
00:39:35.571 --> 00:39:38.904
-Do you have a-- -No, I'm busy.

764
00:39:38.974 --> 00:39:40.908
Sir, could I use a section of your newspaper?

765
00:39:40.976 --> 00:39:43.035
We're late for your doggie spa appointment.

766
00:39:47.716 --> 00:39:50.207
-Here you go. -Thank you, young lady.

767
00:39:50.286 --> 00:39:52.345
No problem. What kind of world would this be...

768
00:39:52.421 --> 00:39:54.889
if we didn't help each other out every once in a while?

769
00:39:54.957 --> 00:39:57.425
Have a good day.

770
00:39:57.493 --> 00:39:59.154
What do you want, Bruiser?

771
00:40:05.000 --> 00:40:06.365
Bruiser, honey, come on.

772
00:40:15.077 --> 00:40:16.271
We have to go. We're late.

773
00:40:18.180 --> 00:40:20.273
We have to get to the doggie spa, remember?

774
00:40:20.349 --> 00:40:23.785
Will it be Swedish or shiatsu massage today?

775
00:40:23.853 --> 00:40:25.821
Come on.

