777
00:40:33.696 --> 00:40:36.221
Redhead, down.

778
00:40:36.298 --> 00:40:38.357
Up next is Stanford Marks...

779
00:40:38.434 --> 00:40:41.028
Southern conservative, NRA spokesman.

780
00:40:41.103 --> 00:40:43.162
How about tulips?

781
00:40:43.239 --> 00:40:47.005
No, no, the calla lily is this year's tulip.

782
00:40:47.076 --> 00:40:49.943
-For weddings? -It's all about the calla.

783
00:40:50.012 --> 00:40:52.037
What would I do without you?

784
00:40:52.114 --> 00:40:54.480
I couldn't do anything without you, Sid.

785
00:40:55.584 --> 00:40:57.279
You're going to get this bill through, Elle.

786
00:40:57.353 --> 00:41:01.449
