We did it! Bill passing!

1045
00:54:51.353 --> 00:54:53.981
Bruiser's Bill!

1046
00:54:54.055 --> 00:54:56.080
Important legislation for our time.

1047
00:55:06.868 --> 00:55:09.132
Bruiser, good work, little guy.

1048
00:55:14.409 --> 00:55:16.138
I would like to conclude this hearing...

1049
00:55:16.211 --> 00:55:18.042
by thanking you all for your testimony--

1050
00:55:18.113 --> 00:55:19.478
Mr. Chairman, sir...

1051
00:55:19.547 --> 00:55:20.707
The chair recognizes...

1052
00:55:20.782 --> 00:55:22.409
the gentlewoman from Massachusetts.

1053
00:55:22.484 --> 00:55:24.748
Mr. Chairman, committee members...

1054
00:55:24.819 --> 00:55:28.346
I would like to thank you for your consideration of this bill.

1055
00:55:28.423 --> 00:55:31.221
However, after further reflection...

1056
00:55:31.292 --> 00:55:34.420
on the budgetary realities of this fiscal year...

1057
00:55:34.496 --> 00:55:37.954
I feel I must withdraw my support for Bruiser's Bill.

1058
00:55:38.032 --> 00:55:40.694
-What? -I concur!

1059
00:55:53.014 --> 00:55:54.982
Everybody, calm down.

1060
00:56:04.259 --> 00:56:06.090
I'm sorry, Bruiser.

1061
00:56:07.862 --> 00:56:10.194
I'm sorry, too, Elle.

1062
00:56:10.265 --> 00:56:12.529
I know you think I've let you down.

1063
00:56:12.600 --> 00:56:15.068
Believe me, I thought about your reaction...

1064
00:56:15.136 --> 00:56:17.161
maybe more than I should have.

1065
00:56:18.940 --> 00:56:21.636
You were outmaneuvered...

1066
00:56:21.709 --> 00:56:23.574
by Grace.

1067
00:56:23.645 --> 00:56:25.408
Grace?

1068
00:56:25.480 --> 00:56:27.914
For the last two sessions she's been pushing...

1069
00:56:27.982 --> 00:56:30.109
this homeowners incentives bill.

1070
00:56:30.185 --> 00:56:32.312
This morning she struck a deal.

1071
00:56:32.387 --> 00:56:36.255
I withdraw my support for Bruiser's Bill.

1072
00:56:36.324 --> 00:56:39.953
Homeowners incentives comes to a vote.

1073
00:56:40.028 --> 00:56:42.019
That was the price and I paid it.

1074
00:56:42.096 --> 00:56:46.192
That's all just deals and trades and secrets.

1075
00:56:49.904 --> 00:56:52.930
That's not what people want.

1076
00:57:01.316 --> 00:57:05.013
Elle...I'm sorry.

1077
00:57:13.795 --> 00:57:15.729
Government of the people...

1078
00:57:15.797 --> 00:57:19.164
by the people, for the people.

1079
00:57:44.158 --> 00:57:47.025
So what's your story?

1080
00:57:47.095 --> 00:57:49.586
Were you even honest?

1081
00:57:50.965 --> 00:57:52.933
I guess you were.

1082
00:57:56.571 --> 00:57:57.799
If you didn't play games...

1083
00:57:57.872 --> 00:58:01.171
then you were probably the only one.

1084
00:58:03.845 --> 00:58:06.575
I just don't know how you did it.

1085
00:58:06.648 --> 00:58:08.980
I don't even mean wearing that silly hat...

1086
00:58:09.050 --> 00:58:10.984
because that was really brave.

1087
00:58:11.052 --> 00:58:13.179
But...

1088
00:58:13.254 --> 00:58:16.189
Just trusting your country.

1089
00:58:16.257 --> 00:58:18.817
Trusting this system...

1090
00:58:21.996 --> 00:58:24.260
Trusting yourself.

1091
00:58:24.332 --> 00:58:26.493
I did.

1092
00:58:41.416 --> 00:58:44.476
Go on. It's full of warm fuzzies.

1093
00:58:44.552 --> 00:58:47.350
With extra fuzz.

1094
00:58:59.634 --> 00:59:02.762
"Elle Woods has amazing lateral delts."

1095
00:59:02.837 --> 00:59:05.738
That was my target muscle group of the month.

1096
00:59:05.807 --> 00:59:08.674
Snaps for Elle's lateral delts.

1097
00:59:24.459 --> 00:59:26.757
"Elle Woods inspires us."

1098
00:59:28.997 --> 00:59:30.794
We even put little hearts over the "ls".

1099
00:59:30.865 --> 00:59:33.857
-I see that. -lt was my idea.

1100
00:59:33.935 --> 00:59:36.062
Thank you, Timothy.

1101
00:59:36.137 --> 00:59:38.605
Thank you, everybody. This is really nice.

1102
00:59:38.673 --> 00:59:42.336
But I just don't think I'm cut out for this.

1103
00:59:42.410 --> 00:59:43.536
Elle, we have a plan.

1104
00:59:43.611 --> 00:59:46.239
Two words for you-- Discharge petition.

1105
00:59:46.314 --> 00:59:48.111
With a couple hundred signatures...

1106
00:59:48.182 --> 00:59:50.116
we can spring Bruiser's Bill from committee...

1107
00:59:50.184 --> 00:59:52.414
straight to the House floor for a vote.

1108
00:59:52.487 --> 00:59:55.854
I don't know. That sounds really complicated.

1109
00:59:55.923 --> 00:59:57.356
You've come farther than any of us...

1110
00:59:57.425 --> 00:59:59.552
while maintaining your bounce and sparkle.

1111
00:59:59.627 --> 01:00:01.288
We never sparkle.

1112
01:00:01.362 --> 01:00:04.456
None of us thought one person could make a difference...

1113
01:00:04.532 --> 01:00:06.693
until you came along.

1114
01:00:08.102 --> 01:00:11.799
If I remember correctly, isn't that 218 signatures?

1115
01:00:11.873 --> 01:00:14.273
It's not that hard.

1116
01:00:14.342 --> 01:00:16.810
Yeah.

1117
01:00:18.112 --> 01:00:19.272
Yeah.

1118
01:00:20.448 --> 01:00:22.643
I guess I know women with more shoes than that.

1119
01:00:22.717 --> 01:00:25.914
Wait, that's me.

1120
01:00:25.987 --> 01:00:27.887
Elle...

1121
01:00:27.955 --> 01:00:30.617
it's time to finish what you started.

1122
01:00:34.462 --> 01:00:36.259
OK, people, a lot on the agenda today.

1123
01:00:36.330 --> 01:00:39.265
Reenie, I'm still waiting on those one-minute floor speeches.

1124
01:00:39.333 --> 01:00:43.326
Timothy, I need recon on that campaign finance reform hearing.

1125
01:00:43.404 --> 01:00:46.100
Grace, status meeting in my office right away.

1126
01:00:49.544 --> 01:00:53.036
I said now.

1127
01:00:57.018 --> 01:00:58.212
Where's my staff?

1128
01:00:58.286 --> 01:01:01.414
They quit, without notice.

1129
01:01:01.489 --> 01:01:03.548
Why?

1130
01:01:05.026 --> 01:01:07.961
Marks and Hauser just filed a petition...

1131
01:01:08.029 --> 01:01:09.428
to discharge Bruiser's Bill.

1132
01:01:09.497 --> 01:01:11.761
I'm pretty sure that's where your staff is...

1133
01:01:11.833 --> 01:01:14.529
Ied by their commander Sorority Sue.

1134
01:01:18.740 --> 01:01:23.143
Petition to discharge HR 2652, aka Bruiser's Bill...

1135
01:01:23.211 --> 01:01:25.179
carried with no objections.

1136
01:01:25.246 --> 01:01:29.205
The petition is filed and available for signature.

1137
01:01:30.518 --> 01:01:32.713
Actually, we are strictly...

1138
01:01:32.787 --> 01:01:36.188
"bring your own" on the discharge petition.

1139
01:01:43.131 --> 01:01:46.658
But it's pink...and scented.

1140
01:01:46.734 --> 01:01:50.135
Gives it something extra, don't you think?

1141
01:01:50.204 --> 01:01:52.695
We've both signed it, as you can see.

1142
01:01:53.941 --> 01:01:56.205
I believe we're being dismissed. Thank you.

1143
01:01:56.277 --> 01:01:58.472
There will be others to come and sign.

1144
01:01:58.546 --> 01:02:00.639
-Don't you like pink? -Come on!

1145
01:02:15.630 --> 01:02:18.599
Up on your feet, people.

1146
01:02:18.666 --> 01:02:21.430
Discharge petition time.

1147
01:02:21.502 --> 01:02:22.901
Upsy-daisy.

1148
01:02:25.339 --> 01:02:28.103
We have our work cut out for us. Let's go.

1149
01:02:30.511 --> 01:02:33.947
OK, we have two signatures. 216 to go.

1150
01:02:34.015 --> 01:02:35.505
I'll break up the country into color codes.

1151
01:02:35.583 --> 01:02:37.517
Timothy, you're teal.

1152
01:02:37.585 --> 01:02:39.780
Reena, you're magenta.

1153
01:02:39.854 --> 01:02:42.118
And Elle is marigold.

1154
01:02:42.190 --> 01:02:43.680
And I've got the Wellington covered.

1155
01:02:43.758 --> 01:02:45.555
37 signatures in residence.

1156
01:02:45.626 --> 01:02:48.322
Sid Post, 37.

1157
01:02:48.396 --> 01:02:51.388
Congress adjourns in 3 weeks. We can't do this alone.

1158
01:02:51.465 --> 01:02:53.399
That's why I'm calling in reinforcements.

1159
01:02:53.467 --> 01:02:54.729
I hope we're talking...

1160
01:02:54.802 --> 01:02:57.134
the brightest political minds in the country.

1161
01:02:59.540 --> 01:03:01.235
We're here!

1162
01:03:06.814 --> 01:03:08.406
Oh, my God!

1163
01:03:10.885 --> 01:03:13.217
Oh, gosh, we can't wait to see the Mall.

1164
01:03:13.287 --> 01:03:14.811
And the Statue of Liberty.

1165
01:03:14.889 --> 01:03:17.289
Everybody, these are my Delta Nu sisters.

1166
01:03:17.358 --> 01:03:18.950
This is Margot and Serena.

1167
01:03:19.026 --> 01:03:22.587
Josh made the cruise boat pull over in Puerto Vallarta.

1168
01:03:22.663 --> 01:03:23.994
I left L.A. right after landing...

1169
01:03:24.065 --> 01:03:26.693
a lateral split in the third quarter dance break.

1170
01:03:26.767 --> 01:03:29.497
It was awesome. I went "Yah!" and "Haah!"

1171
01:03:29.570 --> 01:03:32.061
-That's so great. -Yeah, thanks.

1172
01:03:32.139 --> 01:03:34.664
So, is it time?

1173
01:03:34.742 --> 01:03:36.937
Oh, no, it's not time yet.

1174
01:03:41.349 --> 01:03:44.113
Hello? You're here?

1175
01:03:44.185 --> 01:03:47.177
We'll meet you in the lobby. Let's go.

1176
01:03:50.591 --> 01:03:52.650
Everybody, this is the final member of our team...

1177
01:03:52.727 --> 01:03:53.853
Paulette Parcelle.

1178
01:03:53.928 --> 01:03:56.897
Who's ready to discharge?

1179
01:03:56.964 --> 01:04:01.628
And proposition a bill and...whatever.

1180
01:04:01.702 --> 01:04:03.829
Let's hit the Hill.

1181
01:04:05.072 --> 01:04:07.597
If I could have a moment of your time--

1182
01:04:07.675 --> 01:04:10.576
You could consider something--

1183
01:04:10.645 --> 01:04:13.443
Quadrant 4, corridor 6, have lost one.

1184
01:04:15.349 --> 01:04:18.341
Sorry. How are you?

1185
01:04:18.419 --> 01:04:19.647
If I could have a minute of your time?

1186
01:04:19.720 --> 01:04:21.654
Reena, how are you?

1187
01:04:21.722 --> 01:04:23.212
Has anybody told you about Bruiser's Bill?

1188
01:04:23.291 --> 01:04:24.952
Is it trivial, Congressman Hannenfeld?

1189
01:04:25.026 --> 01:04:27.017
Animals don't have the same reactions...

1190
01:04:27.094 --> 01:04:28.220
to drugs that humans do.

1191
01:04:28.296 --> 01:04:29.422
It's like the time...

1192
01:04:29.497 --> 01:04:31.021
my trainer's sister's cousin's girlfriend...

1193
01:04:31.098 --> 01:04:32.622
gave her overweight Yorkie some phen-fen...

1194
01:04:32.700 --> 01:04:34.292
because she was a little bit fat...

1195
01:04:34.368 --> 01:04:35.767
and it gained three pounds.

1196
01:04:35.836 --> 01:04:38.270
Desired result? I don't think so.

1197
01:04:38.339 --> 01:04:40.466
You know?

1198
01:04:42.243 --> 01:04:44.837
Oh, my dear, gifted woman...

1199
01:04:44.912 --> 01:04:46.174
you tell that Bruiser Woods...

1200
01:04:46.247 --> 01:04:48.909
he can count on the Sunshine State.

1201
01:04:48.983 --> 01:04:51.144
Thank you, Ohio.

1202
01:05:00.861 --> 01:05:03.125
Thank you, Atlanta!

1203
01:05:03.197 --> 01:05:04.994
Who's next?

1204
01:05:05.066 --> 01:05:06.556
You're next!

1205
01:05:09.103 --> 01:05:11.537
We're gonna do it.

1206
01:05:17.745 --> 01:05:19.212
Serena...

1207
01:05:19.280 --> 01:05:22.545
why do they keep sending us to Room 216?

1208
01:05:22.616 --> 01:05:25.585
"lntern Orientation."

1209
01:05:27.021 --> 01:05:29.114
Margot, you're a genius.

1210
01:05:29.190 --> 01:05:30.657
If this doesn't get more signatures...

1211
01:05:30.725 --> 01:05:31.885
I don't know what will.

1212
01:05:34.328 --> 01:05:37.229
Intern class of 2003 on deck!

1213
01:05:43.371 --> 01:05:45.703
Remember, flexibility counts.

1214
01:05:49.377 --> 01:05:51.937
Ready? OK!

1215
01:05:53.180 --> 01:05:55.205
Dogs of the world unite!

1216
01:06:21.142 --> 01:06:22.803
2...4...6...8!

1217
01:06:22.877 --> 01:06:25.175
Sign the petition, win a date!

1218
01:06:25.246 --> 01:06:28.147
Go Bruiser's Bill, go!

1219
01:06:30.751 --> 01:06:32.275
Well, I'm signing.

1220
01:06:34.155 --> 01:06:37.181
Yes, Bob, I know what you're reading.

1221
01:06:37.258 --> 01:06:40.056
Are you kidding?

1222
01:06:40.127 --> 01:06:43.096
Your support has been invaluable to me.

1223
01:06:43.164 --> 01:06:45.894
If it weren't for you, I'd be painting my own posters.

1224
01:06:45.966 --> 01:06:49.231
I don't care if she has two weeks left.

1225
01:06:49.303 --> 01:06:50.998
She could have two years left.

1226
01:06:51.072 --> 01:06:52.630
She won't pull this off.

1227
01:06:52.706 --> 01:06:58.144
I will not be outmaneuvered by this silly little blonde.

1228
01:06:59.914 --> 01:07:02.439
Don't worry, Bob. I'll get her...

1229
01:07:02.516 --> 01:07:04.711
and her little dog, too.

1230
01:07:06.253 --> 01:07:07.982
Even with the entire Wellington...

1231
01:07:08.055 --> 01:07:10.683
and 68 life-changing haircuts under Paulette's belt...

1232
01:07:10.758 --> 01:07:11.884
we're still not even close.

1233
01:07:11.959 --> 01:07:13.688
We got a problem here.

1234
01:07:13.761 --> 01:07:16.924
The bad news is...

1235
01:07:16.997 --> 01:07:18.965
Reena.

1236
01:07:27.942 --> 01:07:32.072
Wow. You look amazing.

1237
01:07:32.146 --> 01:07:35.081
It's just layers and highlights...

1238
01:07:35.149 --> 01:07:36.707
and a cellulose finishing rinse.

1239
01:07:36.784 --> 01:07:38.649
I did it.

1240
01:07:38.719 --> 01:07:40.744
Cool.

1241
01:07:40.821 --> 01:07:42.482
What is the bad news?

1242
01:07:42.556 --> 01:07:45.525
We lost Hannenfeld. We were planning on him...

1243
01:07:45.593 --> 01:07:47.993
to bring Felsen, Parks, and Janowitz on board.

1244
01:07:48.062 --> 01:07:50.155
What are you talking about? I talked to Hannenfeld myself.

1245
01:07:50.231 --> 01:07:52.699
I confirmed with his aide this morning over breakfast.

1246
01:07:52.766 --> 01:07:55.894
I don't know. Somebody must've got to him at lunch.

1247
01:07:56.937 --> 01:07:58.370
It's Grace.

1248
01:07:58.439 --> 01:08:01.033
-Please make sure. -I will. Two weeks?

1249
01:08:01.108 --> 01:08:02.871
I'm looking for Grace Rossiter.

1250
01:08:02.943 --> 01:08:05.707
I just want to know if she's coming back soon.

1251
01:08:05.779 --> 01:08:07.906
Elle. Hi.

1252
01:08:07.982 --> 01:08:09.210
Oh, hi.

1253
01:08:09.283 --> 01:08:11.444
I was going to call you.

1254
01:08:11.519 --> 01:08:14.215
I was looking for Grace.

1255
01:08:14.288 --> 01:08:15.880
The discharge petition.

1256
01:08:15.956 --> 01:08:17.685
We lost Hannenfeld...

1257
01:08:17.758 --> 01:08:19.783
and I was wondering if Grace knew anything about it.

1258
01:08:19.860 --> 01:08:21.987
None of that is important anymore.

1259
01:08:22.062 --> 01:08:24.462
Could I speak with you for a moment?

1260
01:08:24.532 --> 01:08:26.363
Sure.

1261
01:08:33.607 --> 01:08:35.939
You did it, Elle. You won.

1262
01:08:36.010 --> 01:08:38.808
You can collect Bruiser's mom anytime you like.

1263
01:08:38.879 --> 01:08:40.244
What?

1264
01:08:40.314 --> 01:08:43.112
If you promise not to be disappointed in me again...

1265
01:08:43.184 --> 01:08:46.551
I'll tell you. I pulled a few strings.

1266
01:08:46.620 --> 01:08:51.057
C'est Magnifique is releasing all of their test animals.

1267
01:08:51.125 --> 01:08:52.615
All of them?

1268
01:08:52.693 --> 01:08:54.490
All of them. And what's more...

1269
01:08:54.562 --> 01:08:55.893
they have been so impressed...

1270
01:08:55.963 --> 01:08:58.261
with how you've handled yourself down here...

1271
01:08:58.332 --> 01:09:02.268
they want you on board as head of their legal department.

1272
01:09:02.336 --> 01:09:03.769
It's a very generous offer.

1273
01:09:03.837 --> 01:09:06.101
I don't know.

1274
01:09:06.173 --> 01:09:07.640
You did it.

1275
01:09:07.708 --> 01:09:10.268
You did what you came here to do.

1276
01:09:10.344 --> 01:09:13.211
Yeah, but what about the discharge petition?

1277
01:09:13.280 --> 01:09:15.373
This isn't about just one animal...

1278
01:09:15.449 --> 01:09:16.575
it's all of the animals.

1279
01:09:16.650 --> 01:09:19.312
I agree, but you've got a great team in place.

1280
01:09:19.386 --> 01:09:20.910
They can carry on without you.

1281
01:09:20.988 --> 01:09:23.650
C'est Magnifique wants you up there by Monday.

1282
01:09:23.724 --> 01:09:26.989
You can go home.

1283
01:09:27.061 --> 01:09:29.655
Congratulations, Elle.

1284
01:09:29.730 --> 01:09:31.891
Wow. Thank you. Thanks for doing that.

1285
01:09:31.966 --> 01:09:33.831
Well, sure.

1286
01:09:36.937 --> 01:09:40.338
We have to stick together, us Washington blondes.

1287
01:09:40.407 --> 01:09:43.171
Do you know who Representative Hannenfeld...

1288
01:09:43.244 --> 01:09:45.872
had lunch with today in the members dining room?

1289
01:09:47.248 --> 01:09:50.149
I skipped lunch today. Had a facial.

1290
01:09:50.217 --> 01:09:52.685
OK. Thanks.

1291
01:09:52.753 --> 01:09:54.812
I'll call you about that.

1292
01:09:54.888 --> 01:09:56.378
Yeah.

1293
01:10:07.501 --> 01:10:10.163
Emmett, I know you're probably in Case Law class right now...

1294
01:10:10.237 --> 01:10:12.228
but call me back when you get this.

1295
01:10:12.306 --> 01:10:14.638
I think I'm coming home.

1296
01:10:14.708 --> 01:10:16.573
But it's a good thing.

1297
01:10:16.644 --> 01:10:19.807
Maybe. Call me back.

1298
01:10:32.059 --> 01:10:33.993
Will you leave us alone now?

1299
01:10:34.061 --> 01:10:35.653
Excuse me?

1300
01:10:35.729 --> 01:10:37.720
I know you've been working against us...

1301
01:10:37.798 --> 01:10:39.060
and I know somehow it's personal.

1302
01:10:39.133 --> 01:10:41.567
-You don't like me. -Clearly.

1303
01:10:41.635 --> 01:10:45.264
If I leave Washington, will you call off the fight...

1304
01:10:45.339 --> 01:10:46.806
and let Bruiser's Bill have a fair shot?

1305
01:10:46.874 --> 01:10:50.332
Your bill is trivial to me. I have my own agenda.

1306
01:10:50.411 --> 01:10:53.812
Like the homeowners bill you pushed through at our expense?

1307
