1499
01:21:52.138 --> 01:21:54.003
facing us today.

1500
01:21:54.074 --> 01:21:57.407
Ladies and gentlemen of both Houses...

1501
01:21:57.477 --> 01:22:02.176
I give you Ms. Elle Woods.

1502
01:22:35.782 --> 01:22:37.682
It's all yours.

1503
01:22:42.122 --> 01:22:44.090
Thank you, Congresswoman.

1504
01:22:45.725 --> 01:22:48.125
Hello, everyone, my name is Elle Woods...

1505
01:22:48.194 --> 01:22:50.992
and I'm here to speak to you today...

1506
01:22:51.064 --> 01:22:54.761
about a piece of legislation called Bruiser's Bill.

1507
01:23:05.278 --> 01:23:07.838
But you know...

1508
01:23:07.914 --> 01:23:11.145
today is supposed to be about education.

1509
01:23:11.217 --> 01:23:15.654
So instead, I want to tell you about the education...

1510
01:23:15.722 --> 01:23:17.849
you all have given me over the past three months.

1511
01:23:17.924 --> 01:23:19.824
What about Bruiser's Bill? We still need 15 signatures.

1512
01:23:19.893 --> 01:23:21.121
She's blowing it.

1513
01:23:21.194 --> 01:23:24.186
I came to Washington to help my dog Bruiser...

1514
01:23:24.264 --> 01:23:25.697
and somewhere along the way...

1515
01:23:25.765 --> 01:23:29.667
I learned a really unexpected lesson.

1516
01:23:30.970 --> 01:23:34.235
I know what you're thinking-- Who is this girl?

1517
01:23:34.307 --> 01:23:37.572
And what could this simple, small-town girl from Bel Air...

1518
01:23:37.644 --> 01:23:40.772
have to say to all of us? I'll tell you.

1519
01:23:40.847 --> 01:23:45.113
It's about something that's bigger than me...

1520
01:23:45.185 --> 01:23:48.279
or any single act of legislation.

1521
01:23:48.354 --> 01:23:51.414
This is about a matter that should be at...

1522
01:23:51.491 --> 01:23:55.188
the highest importance to every American--

1523
01:23:56.329 --> 01:23:58.729
My hair.

1524
01:24:01.234 --> 01:24:02.667
There's this salon in Beverly Hills.

1525
01:24:02.735 --> 01:24:06.535
It's really fancy and beautiful.

1526
01:24:06.606 --> 01:24:08.540
It's impossible to get an appointment.

1527
01:24:08.608 --> 01:24:10.940
Unless you're Julia Roberts or from "Friends"...

1528
01:24:11.010 --> 01:24:12.671
you can just forget it.

1529
01:24:12.745 --> 01:24:16.545
But one day, they called me. They had an opening.

1530
01:24:16.616 --> 01:24:18.880
So I was going to finally get the chance...

1531
01:24:18.952 --> 01:24:21.079
to sit in one of those sacred beauty chairs.

1532
01:24:21.154 --> 01:24:23.145
I was so excited.

1533
01:24:23.223 --> 01:24:26.351
Then the colorist...

1534
01:24:26.426 --> 01:24:29.725
gave me Brassy Brigitte instead of Harlow Honey.

1535
01:24:29.796 --> 01:24:33.926
The shampoo girl washed my hair with spiral perm solution...

1536
01:24:34.000 --> 01:24:36.992
instead of color-intensive moisturizing shampoo.

1537
01:24:37.070 --> 01:24:40.267
Finally, the stylist...

1538
01:24:40.340 --> 01:24:44.538
gave me a bob...with bangs.

1539
01:24:45.578 --> 01:24:49.105
Suffice to say, it was just wrong.

1540
01:24:49.182 --> 01:24:53.778
All wrong. For me, you know?

1541
01:24:53.853 --> 01:24:55.218
First I was angry.

1542
01:24:55.288 --> 01:24:58.746
And then I realized my anger was completely misdirected.

1543
01:24:58.825 --> 01:25:00.884
This wasn't the salon's fault.

1544
01:25:00.960 --> 01:25:03.656
I had sat there and witnessed this injustice...

1545
01:25:03.730 --> 01:25:05.425
and had let it happen.

1546
01:25:05.498 --> 01:25:10.265
I didn't get involved in the process.

1547
01:25:10.336 --> 01:25:14.067
I forgot to use my voice.

1548
01:25:14.140 --> 01:25:18.236
I forgot to believe in myself.

1549
01:25:18.311 --> 01:25:20.575
But now I know better.

1550
01:25:20.647 --> 01:25:26.711
I know that one honest voice can be louder than a crowd.

1551
01:25:26.786 --> 01:25:31.621
I know that if we lose our voice...

1552
01:25:31.691 --> 01:25:35.422
or if we let those who speak on our behalf...

1553
01:25:35.495 --> 01:25:38.123
compromise our voice...

1554
01:25:38.198 --> 01:25:42.362
then, this country...

1555
01:25:42.435 --> 01:25:45.199
this country is in for a really bad haircut.

1556
01:25:49.842 --> 01:25:52.174
So speak up, America.

1557
01:25:52.245 --> 01:25:53.803
Speak up!

1558
01:25:53.880 --> 01:25:57.281
Speak up for the home of the brave.

1559
01:25:57.350 --> 01:26:00.979
Speak up for the land of the free gift with purchase.

1560
01:26:01.054 --> 01:26:05.616
Speak up, America. Speak up!

1561
01:26:08.461 --> 01:26:10.395
And remember...

1562
01:26:10.463 --> 01:26:12.556
